        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 29 at 5:53PM MDT by NWS Billings MT</headline>
        <description>At 553 PM MDT, A trained spotter reported nickel size hail in a
strong thunderstorm 15 miles south of Sheridan, moving east at 20
mph.

HAZARD...Nickel size hail.

SOURCE...Trained spotters reported.

IMPACT...Minor damage to outdoor objects is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Banner.
</description>
